  "edu-006": { steps: ["Create a 15-page A4 learning activity bundle: 5 literacy activities, 5 numeracy activities, and 5 general knowledge activities for ages 4–8.", "Use a bright, engaging design — full colour with simple instructions readable by a teacher or parent.", "Design 5 literacy pages: letter matching, word search (5 simple words), fill in the blank sentences, picture-word matching, and a story sequencing activity.", "Design 5 numeracy pages: counting objects up to 20, simple addition using pictures, skip counting, shape recognition, and a money activity for UK coins.", "Design 5 general knowledge pages: map colouring activity, animal matching, colour mixing, weather journaling, and a seasons sorting page.", "Export all as individual A4 PDFs at 300 DPI and as a single bundled PDF for easy download.", "Create playful classroom or home learning desk mockups and list with learning activities, printable worksheets, and KS1 educational keywords."] },
