  "edu-010": { steps: ["Create a 12-card bundle of A5 printable STEM activity instruction cards covering: 3 science experiments, 3 engineering challenges, 3 maths puzzles, and 3 technology/coding activities.", "Use a bold, activity-guide style — numbered steps, materials list, and clean kid-friendly illustrations.", "Design 3 science experiment cards: volcano baking soda, colour-mixing experiment, and growing cress seeds — each with materials, steps, and what happened section.", "Design 3 engineering challenge cards: build a bridge with pasta, design a paper tower, and make a waterproof shelter — with constraints and goal fields.", "Design 3 maths puzzle cards (pattern challenge, measurement hunt, shape sort) and 3 technology cards (screen-free coding activity, algorithm treasure hunt, binary bracelet).", "Export all as A5 double-sided PDFs at 300 DPI and as A4 two-up layout for easy cutting.", "Create school activity station mockups and list with STEM activities, science experiment cards, and KS1 STEM keywords."] },
